A vintage-style illustration of a curious detective with a magnifying glass examining a mysterious golden trophy or award badge sitting on an ornate wooden desk, surrounded by scattered papers and old newspapers. The scene is bathed in warm sepia tones with dramatic shadows cast by a green banker's lamp. The detective's expression shows equal parts skepticism and intrigue. Dust motes float in the amber light streaming through venetian blinds, creating noir atmosphere. The trophy gleams suspiciously bright against the muted, aged color palette of browns, creams, and deep forest greens.
